Pro Shop Discount
As a member, you save 10% on all in-stock items in our pro shop. This excludes rackets, paddles, and items under $20.

As a member, you can attend our free clinics for pickleball and tennis to enhance your skills and level up your game.

Our facility boasts and 11 tennis courts and 8 top of the line pickleball courts all equipped with high-quality lighting for uninterrupted play day or night.
Fitness Classes
You’re welcome to join any member organized workouts or strength training sessions.  Schedule a private training session to increase your fitness level.
House Account Privileges
Add the cost of your extras to your monthly house account for easy and convenient payment for you and your family.
